'''Space poker''' was a game. The indivudals [[Stuart Zissu]] and [[Granit]] played a game of space poker on [[Da'nor]], and they used the game phrases "two turbos" and "one propulsion" while competing to win. Granit ended the game with a full planetary system, which beat Stuart's three satellites.<ref name="Star Wars Science Adventures: Journey Across Planet X" /> [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] pilots stationed on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]], including [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], played space poker, although no one there could beat Stuart.

